Project Overview

This project consists of two major tasks:
Dataset Processing and Analysis
Translation using Large Language Models (LLM)
The goal is to preprocess an English-Hindi parallel dataset, filter high-quality sentence pairs, and evaluate translation performance using a modern LLM.

